{"tid":2514303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華駐法使館促美台停官方往來","createTime":"2021-05-03T07:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T07:30:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"37d2a0fcfef1e591f886556ecfae6137e3f6532f","tid":2514303,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:26:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210503/LGMFPUUBUNGMDPYNOSV76RSYZM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210503%2FLGMFPUUBUNGMDPYNOSV76RSYZM%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOBURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=5ee1911e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210503%2FLGMFPUUBUNGMDPYNOSV76RSYZM%2F&h=319e7f91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210503/LGMFPUUBUNGMDPYNOSV76RSYZM/</a><br />\n<br />\n華駐法使館促美台停官方往來<br />\n<br />\n美國駐法國大使館早前邀請台灣駐法代表進入官邸午餐，是美台自1979年斷交以來首次。中國駐法大使館昨在官網回應，指台灣是中國不可分割的一部份，堅決反對美方的行為，促美方立即停止任何形式的美台官方來往。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nmOA-2AtAXntcFOFgSewl8V-TCs=/510x165/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OM5MF564XNB45DKBDZAJSBII3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnmOA-2AtAXntcFOFgSewl8V-TCs%3D%2F510x165%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOM5MF564XNB45DKBDZAJSBII3A.jpg&h=d3d20f66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「濱州號」連續兩日在台日附近海域出現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華護衞艦入東海 日台監視<br />\n<br />\n中國駐法大使館。。。。。。。場。<br />\n<br />\n另外，根據日本防衞省統合幕僚監部報告，中國解放軍導彈護衞艦「濱州號」上周五（4月30日）起，連續兩日在台日附近海域出現。濱州號上周五凌晨先在宮古島東北150公里出現，沿宮古水道向東南航行，進入太平洋，日方派出預警機和護衞艦監視。到了前日，濱州號經過台灣基隆和日本沖繩縣「與那國島」之間的海域，北上進入東海，日本海上自衞隊護衞艦和台灣的基隆級驅逐艦分別監視濱州號。據稱，這是防衞省首次公佈中國軍艦通過與那國島與台灣之間海域。<br />\n<br />\n對於早前解放軍航母山東號在南海進行訓練，解放軍海軍發言人高秀成昨指，例行訓練是根據山東號編隊的年度工作計劃，他強調中國海軍日後將按計劃常態化組織類似演訓。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/央視"},{"pid":"07f7287d2dbdad3b1d385067ed1e16650d522ef7","tid":2514303,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:27:14.000Z","msg":"繼續叫春"},{"pid":"b7240c559504a71f336f9d7fc79cd0844b69dbd4","tid":2514303,"uid":224882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:28:40.000Z","msg":"濱州號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0bc2122f8404012430a8fb936ddcfc443dae0f","tid":2514303,"uid":183090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:30:18.000Z","msg":"支那：你地唔準出街拍拖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}